{"tid":2294584,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Joaquin Phoenix 正洽談與《祖孽》、 《仲夏魘》 導演合作新戲《Beau is Afraid》","createTime":"2020-11-21T06:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T15:53:50.000Z","uid":157092,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ba4fa5b4e71d63eeffe2778c7833e03d84f6f0c4","tid":2294584,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"Joaquin Phoenix In Talks To Star In Ari Aster&rsquo;s &lsquo;Beau Is Afraid&rsquo; (EXCLUSIVE)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://discussingfilm.net/2020/11/20/joaquin-phoenix-in-talks-to-star-in-ari-asters-beau-is-afraid-exclusive/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscussingfilm.net%2F2020%2F11%2F20%2Fjoaquin-phoenix-in-talks-to-star-in-ari-asters-beau-is-afraid-exclusive%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3yWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=c429f409\" target=\"_blank\">https://discussingfilm.net/2020/11/20/joaquin-phoenix-in-talks-to-star-in-ari-asters-beau-is-afraid-exclusive/</a><br />\n<br />\nFilm fans, prepare for a splendid collaboration between two icons. Joaquin Phoenix is in talks to star in Ari Aster&rsquo;s upcoming film&nbsp;Beau is Afraid.<br />\nPer sources, the film was described to me as a surrealist horror film set in an alternate present. If Joaquin Phoenix signs on, he will play the lead role of Beau. Beau is described as an extremely anxious but pleasant-looking man who has a fraught relationship with his overbearing mother, their relationship is affected from the fact that he never knew his father.<br />\nThis will likely be Ari Aster&rsquo;s next film with the project said to be a priority for himself. He will write, direct, and produce the film with the project set to go through his production company Square Peg.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">The film&rsquo;s synopsis sounds&hellip;crazy! An anxious man (Joaquin Phoenix) learns of the death of his mother under mysterious circumstances and upon traveling home makes an alarming discovery about his past. During his journey, he runs into various crazy supernatural threats.</span>"},{"pid":"bc3c4d46b83326f24cf6892e29c2bdf58058ff88","tid":2294584,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T06:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好正"},{"pid":"cccb638172d701de909f7ef92a68c6cd7d2b661b","tid":2294584,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9575adc553642269860170891a2538922573bdf","tid":2294584,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8980aa6f65aba36be857fd6f8b604e4a60cd5ee7","tid":2294584,"uid":66893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好開心"},{"pid":"d2ab0cc6e3f2311485374a6052aa9bb2ef280e78","tid":2294584,"uid":66893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8980aa6f65aba36be857fd6f8b604e4a60cd5ee7","tid":2294584,"uid":66893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/b